title: 10 Days Under the Sea Adventures of Diana Salinger
description:
10 Days Under the Sea: Adventures of Diana Salinger


This Is a Pre-Release so there is not alot to find about the game

 After days of travel, the compass needle has led us to a secret pirate grotto on a small island in the Caribbean Sea.

 Here, in a mass of stolen but long forgotten treasures, the 1st part of the magic compass is hidden.


System Requirements
windows XP/98/me
